description:
Penn trans swimmer’s teammates speak to OutKick. Fauci: Demand proof relatives are vaccinated this Christmas. OutKick's Joe Kinsey joins C&B to discuss his exclusive interview with the UPenn female teammates of the male swimmer breaking women's swimming records. Gavin Newsom gets defensive over California crime wave. C&B take calls.
